# +page.server.js ğŸ“¡

To fetch data securely on the server:

```javascript
// src/routes/blog/+page.server.js
export function load() {
  return {
    posts: db.getPosts()
  };
}
```
Access it in `+page.svelte` via `export let data`.

# Form Actions ğŸ“

Handle form submissions without API endpoints.

```javascript
// +page.server.js
export const actions = {
  default: async ({ request }) => {
    const data = await request.formData();
    // save data
  }
};
```

```html
<form method="POST">...</form>
```

# +server.js ğŸ”Œ

Create standalone API endpoints (JSON).

```javascript
// src/routes/api/users/+server.js
export function GET() {
  return new Response(JSON.stringify({ name: 'User' }));
}
```
Access via `/api/users`.

